{"tid":2139252,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"與曼聯擦肩的11巨星陣容：這套343實在太強！","createTime":"2020-08-04T07:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T11:08:16.000Z","uid":147522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6992bd0421df6953cc22bd0ff84fbf90dedc863a","tid":2139252,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScMf1AC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScMf1AC.jpg&h=428a3d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《每日郵報》評出曼聯錯過的11人巨星陣容。<br />\n　　<br />\n施治（Petr Čech）<br />\n費格遜（Alex Ferguson）自傳回憶說：「2003年我去雷恩看他比賽，我們當時認為他對英超來說太年輕了，他當時19歲，我心裡說：他太年輕了。」<br />\n<br />\n拉莫斯（Sergio Ramos）<br />\n2015年曼聯曾有機會簽下拉莫斯，但後者最終留在了皇馬。<br />\n<br />\n雲迪積克（Virgil van Dijk）<br />\n前曼聯教練梅倫斯丁曾稱，2018年紅魔考察了修咸頓的雲迪積克，但對他興趣不足。<br />\n　　<br />\n泰利（John Terry）<br />\n泰利從小是曼聯球迷，1998年曾被邀請參觀訓練基地，但他選擇了車路士，因為對藍軍感覺合適。<br />\n　　<br />\n巴爾（Gareth Bale）<br />\n2007年曼聯想簽下修咸頓的巴爾，但熱刺最終得手。<br />\n　　<br />\n卻奧斯（Toni Kroos）<br />\n莫耶斯（David Moyes）曾試圖簽下卻奧斯，但他下台了，雲高爾（Louis van Gaal）上任後，交易不了了之。<br />\n　　<br />\n艾辛（Michael Essien）<br />\n17歲的艾辛曾經到曼聯試訓，紅魔也想簽下他，但因為勞工證而未能成功。<br />\n<br />\n普列錫（Christian Pulisic）<br />\n在多蒙特踢球時，他曾多次被球探推薦給曼聯。<br />\n　　<br />\n夏蘭特（Erling Haland）<br />\n蘇斯克查曾想簽下夏蘭特，但因為經理人拉奧拿的原因，曼聯沒能達成交易。<br />\n　　<br />\n舒利亞（Alan Shearer）<br />\n1996年舒利亞曾有機會加盟曼聯，但他最終選擇了家鄉球隊紐卡素。<br />\n<br />\n朗拿甸奴（Ronaldinho）<br />\n2003年曼聯幾乎簽下朗拿甸奴，但巴西人最後時刻與巴塞簽約。"},{"pid":"f83891efa7ad110a5e329c5702414cd9857a71d8","tid":2139252,"uid":302390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"真係咁樣打應該會係咁失波"},{"pid":"ca8737425aa613cac8c96999906e57c349acc04b","tid":2139252,"uid":41352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f83891efa7ad110a5e329c5702414cd9857a71d8","tid":2139252,"uid":302390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"真係咁樣打應該會係咁失波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"3個中堅上哂去頂角球，巴爾跑得夠快都回唔切防"},{"pid":"f3e1be6a4b8fb7802782df415afc683a437cd613","tid":2139252,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"仲有施丹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2556a541a46edd4a034fd4d729b5f31c64630add","tid":2139252,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴果套呢？"},{"pid":"467f2729c745ab415fe3fd10221acd23a7bcd4a3","tid":2139252,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"傳曼聯勁d"},{"pid":"9dc16b1d8f4f4f26135aac42e1f69f13c5c84bd9","tid":2139252,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2556a541a46edd4a034fd4d729b5f31c64630add","tid":2139252,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴果套呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:56:39.000Z","msg":"伊巴連波衫都著左都可以變險簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e64fe2111bc0e13f111215eb46d5c03621b054","tid":2139252,"uid":240975,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2556a541a46edd4a034fd4d729b5f31c64630add","tid":2139252,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴果套呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5vtVhtA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vtVhtA.jpg&h=5dd5849a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1f5cd311dabf68e502ed19de822151fcaa92d0e","tid":2139252,"uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35e64fe2111bc0e13f111215eb46d5c03621b054","tid":2139252,"uid":240975,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2556a541a46edd4a034fd4d729b5f31c64630add","tid":2139252,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴果套呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:16:55.000Z","m